### Implement Custom Authentication Strategy

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/tools/claude-plugin/skills/payload/reference/ADVANCED.md

Create custom authentication strategies beyond default password-based auth. Define authentication logic with access to headers and payload instance. Strategies are attached to collection auth configuration.

```typescript
import type { CollectionConfig, Strategy } from 'payload'

const customStrategy: Strategy = {
  name: 'custom',
  authenticate: async ({ payload, headers }) => {
    const token = headers.get('authorization')?.split(' ')[1]
    if (!token) return { user: null }

    const user = await verifyToken(token)
    return { user }
  },
}

export const Users: CollectionConfig = {
  slug: 'users',
  auth: {
    strategies: [customStrategy],
  },
  fields: [],
}
```

